data.description: This brick ranch has a park-like setting and is butted up with views of Driscoll Park. Very spacious rooms and a partially finished, high and dry, walk-out, daylight basement. Hardwoods throughout, large eat-in kitchen, oversized one-car garage with workspace, two-car covered parking, loads of off-street parking, covered pavilion, mature treed landscaping. The location of this home is stellar with a picturesque setting that is quiet yet convenient to shopping and highways. Ready for you to move in and make your own.
